title: The Pink Jungle (1968 - USA) [James Garner, George Kennedy]
description:
The Pink Jungle (1968 - USA)

Action / Adventure / Comedy

director . . . . Delbert Mann
starring . . . . James Garner, Eva Renzi, George Kennedy
 
http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0063429/


Left without transportation in a South American village during an ad campaign shoot, photographer Ben Morris and model Alison Duguesne join forces with Sammy Ryderbeit, who has a map showing the location of a mythical diamond mine. Accompanied by clever Australian Dennis McCune, who claims to have known the map's owner, the group is stranded again after he takes their equipment. The three struggle to catch up with McCune and find the treasure.
